{"name":"Nicholas Castino","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Fenwick, Vanguards, Skeletron","alignment":"Lawful Good","hitDice":"15","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":8,"otherArmorDesc":"16 (Genetic Modification)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"18","intPoints":"20","wisPoints":"16","chaPoints":"8","blindsight":"45","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON]'s spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC [INT SAVE], [INT ATK] to hit). His focus is his medkit. [MON] has the following spells prepared:\n\n> Cantrips (at will): _Control Flames, Shocking Grasp, Acid Splash, Prestidigitation, Eldritch Blast_\n> 1st level (4 slots): _Ray of Sickness, Sleep, Absorb Elements, Tasha's Caustic Brew_\n> 2nd level (3 slots): _Misty Step, Enhance Ability, Wither & Bloom_\n> 3rd level (2 slots): _Slow, Sending, Haste_"},{"name":"Magic Resistance","desc":"[MON] has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects."},{"name":"Outbreak","desc":"At the start of their turn, if an uninfected creature is within a 10ft. radius of another infected creature, they must make a **DC [INT SAVE]** Con save or get infected with Contagion as well."}],"actions":[{"name":"Bioweapon","desc":"[MON] unleashes a virus (PAX-30) that infects a creature within 10ft. This attack acts similarly to the spell Contagion, but creatures take [1d12] poison damage when they fail the saving throw."},{"name":"Genetic Reshuffle","desc":"[MON] completely scrambles the DNA of a creature within a 120ft radius. If they fail (or willingly fail) a **DC [INT SAVE]** Charisma save, Nick can:\n\n> * Change one of their ability score by up to 8 (min 1)\n> * Add or remove a skill proficiency or saving throw\n> * Modify their speed by up to 15ft.\n> * Add or remove a resistance, weakness, or immunity\n> * Swap two ability scores\n\nGiven the fragile nature of DNA, this deals [4d6] force damage and lasts for an hour."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Vanguard MK-V","desc":"[MON] wields an experimental, futuristic med-kit. [MON] may:\n\n> * Allow a creature to use all their hit die\n> * End a disease or conditions on a creature\n> * End any effects reducing a creature's max HP\n> * Cast revivify"}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"con","order":2},{"name":"wis","order":4},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"medicine","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"nature","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"survival","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Nick","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}